<h2 id=3D"ez_file_size-Description">Description</h2>
<p><code>ez_file_size()</code> is a Twig helper (Twig filter) which is most=
ly a byte calculator. It will convert a number from byte to the correct suf=
fix (from B to EB). The output pattern will also vary with the current lang=
uage of the site access (e.g. choosing between coma or point pattern).</p>
<p>It returns a string.</p>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-inf=
ormation">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-informa=
tion-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p>The byte factor is 1000 instead of 1024 to be more familiar for users.</=
p>
</div>
</div>
<h2 id=3D"ez_file_size-PrototypeandArguments">Prototype and Arguments</h2>
<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong>integer <strong>number_of_bytes</strong>|ez_file_=
size( integer <strong>number_of_decimal</strong> )</p>
